{"tid":2109792,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【本土史】皇家學會研究，香港歷史嘅十點真相","createTime":"2020-07-15T12:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T01:52:09.000Z","uid":276716,"like":65,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"a0705ab2ea9fe7ffc9d7398ae415a11e3221fd70","tid":2109792,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T12:39:14.000Z","msg":"完結香港基金搞咗個「香港地方志中心」，搵咗班所謂學者，話要為香港「編撰」歷史。佢哋目的係乜，大家心中有數。<br />\n<br />\n呢度，我會引用皇家亞洲學會期刊嘅文章，為真正香港史留低個紀錄。我相信不久將來，呢一系列文章，好快就會冇得睇。<br />\n<br />\n1. 香港最早原住民係南島民族，遠早於漢人，蜑家人就係佢哋後裔，仍然住喺香港。<br />\n&ldquo;Their (Austronesians) survival may have lasted......as late as Sung dynasty, the date...... when Chinese peasants first began to migrate into this region&rdquo;<br />\nHong Kong before British by S.F. Balfour<br />\n<br />\n2. 中華帝國係「殖民者」，而且中華農業族群（即所謂「漢人」）殖民香港係好遲先發生，歷史並冇想像中長。<br />\n&ldquo;It is important to distinguish between the Chinese conquest .......and its colonisation by peasants.......Its colonisation by Chinese peasants did not occur until over 1000 years later and is in fact a comparatively recent development.&rdquo;<br />\nHong Kong before British by S.F. Balfour<br />\n<br />\n3. 李鄭屋古墓唔代表有中國人喺香港住，中國人定居香港嘅歷史最早只可以追溯到唐王朝後期。<br />\n&ldquo;Although one Chinese type grave......has been found in New Kowloon......there is no evidence of Chinese settlement before the end of Tang.&rdquo;<br />\nHong Kong before the Chinese by K.M.A Barnett <br />\n<br />\n4. 由漢王朝覆滅，至唐王朝，中華從未控制香港。直至十世紀，香港得好少中國人。<br />\n&ldquo;When Han dynasty broke up......and right up to Tang dynasty the chinese never regained their imperial hold over the South coast. The region was therefore left to the semi-tutored aborigines......until almost 10th century the pure Chinese population of this region must have been comparatively small.&rdquo;<br />\nHong Kong before British by S.F. Balfour<br />\n<br />\n5. 香港一帶島嶼，直至元王朝，仍然由水上人完全獨立控制，而且有武裝守衛。<br />\n&ldquo;At this time Lantao and other islands, Hong Kong harbour itself and the peninsulas that just into Mirs Bay were controlled by boat-people...They were still unassimilated, and independent enough to require strong garrisons to keep them quiet, at the beginning of the Yuan dynasty&rdquo;<br />\nDo Words from Extinct Pre-Chinese Languages Survive in Hong Kong Place-Names? by K.M.A Barnett<br />\n<br />\n6. 明王朝滅亡後，遺將管治港九新界十年之久，與廣東嘅清兵作軍事對抗。<br />\n&ldquo;A former officer of the Ming, Li Man Wing, held this area on his own account, between 1647 and his surrender to the new dynasty in 1656.&rdquo;<br />\nThe Hong Kong Region by James Hayes<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7. 鄭氏家族以香港為根據地，盤據珠江口至少五十年，不受清政府管轄<br />\n&ldquo;Cheng Lin Fuk and his son, Cheng Yat , both notorious pirates from Tai Yu Shan, who terrorized the Chu Kong estuary during the latter half of the 18th century.&rdquo;<br />\nFan Lau and its Fort: an Historical Perspective by Armando Da Silva<br />\n<br />\n8. 雖然清國自稱有喺香港島駐兵，但英國接管時，乜痕跡到搵唔到。<br />\n&ldquo;There does not seem to have been any civil or military establishment on Hong Kong island when it was taken over&rdquo;<br />\nHong Kong Island before 1841 by James Hayes<br />\n<br />\n9. 香港原住民長期支援英軍，令英國人覺得有道義責任要保護香港人免受清國威脅。呢個係英國接管香港嘅其中一個原因。<br />\n&ldquo;The retention of Hong Kong would be an act of justice and protection to the Native population upon which we have been so long dependent for assistance and supply...... they cannot be abandoned without the most fatal consequences.&rdquo;<br />\nHong Kong Island before 1841 by James Hayes<br />\n<br />\n10. 九龍唔係漢語，唔係「九條龍」咁解。香港地名常見嘅「馬」、「黃竹」、「黃麻」、「網」、「朗」、「瀝」、「白」都唔係漢語。<br />\nDo Words from Extinct Pre-Chinese Languages Survive in Hong Kong Place-Names? by K.M.A Barnett"},{"pid":"d34172b6061c9215c8ea5da8f27d5fa3c93e2bf8","tid":2109792,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T12:40:56.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"4671d47fc62715500a74412eedc9d334b1be3df3","tid":2109792,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T12:41:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除